name: first_queen_luna
description: After all those women, only a selected few stayed in the castle, and from them fewer survived the erotic follies of the king, the night the king died only three remained, where only the cyan hair remained as the only candidate, to embrace the true king's objective.

name: old_maiden_yekaterina
description: Katia always feared loneliness, she delved in the harshest places since she was really young as long as there was the warm of people, the church, sending anything they could, wouldn't moralize while battling, even if they had to give pointless titles as doctors, in war ground.

name: parlourmaid_primi
description: Grown from the hungry ground, she was enlisted for the kaás academy as a soldier from times she can't even remember, those wars inevitably led her to the moist mud, where a wealthy mage offered her another life, with one condition.

name: yelendria
description: With Piervyy gone and a price to her head, there was nothing she had left, in her final moment, an erased knight without name planted a seed of an extinct flower, the knight's last breath grew the blooming spell. At last, there was nothing else to lose.

name: mariae
description: After an outstretched time, she held her might in one hand with great power, she came from too far, and the same night she wore the crown, her sister, and only sister, fallen in blood by an unknown blade, furiously, she sent the last members of the Kaás academy to search for the killer.
